    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>What about this at your thread's beginings?</p>\n\n<pre><code>if (Thread.currentThread().getName().split(\"-\").length &gt; 1) {\n    String threadName = Thread.currentThread().getName();\n    threadName = \"thread\" + threadName.split(\"-\")[3];\n    Thread.currentThread().setName(threadName);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then in your logback.xml:</p>\n\n<pre><code>[%-8thread] %msg%n\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>... and you'll get something like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>[main    ] Process started\n[thread1 ] Thread started\n[thread2 ] Thread started\n[thread1 ] Thread ended\n[thread1 ] Thread started\n[thread2 ] Thread ended\n[thread2 ] Thread started\n[thread1 ] Thread ended\n[thread2 ] Thread ended\n[thread3 ] Thread ended\n[thread4 ] Thread ended\n[thread5 ] Thread ended\n[main    ] Process ended\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1518185,
      "reputation" : 11597,
      "user_id" : 1418643,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 75,
