    "question_id" : 5924112,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To print the 7 last characters and Rightpad with spaces:</p>\n\n<pre><code>[%-7.7thread] \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Output:</p>\n\n<pre><code>14:22:43.097 [main   ] DEBUG \n14:22:43.341 [main   ] INFO  \n14:22:43.341 [main   ] INFO  \n14:22:45.399 [-target] INFO  \n</code></pre>\n"
